" tone that celebrates \"Coastal Comfort\" and \"Cultural Romance.\"  Vibe word: Sussegad.  ---  ### Section 4 - Core Features & Functionality  1. Modular \"Bento\" Grid Layout - A homepage architecture that organizes content into clean, responsive blocks (Menu, Story, Reservations, Shop) for instant scannability. 2. \"Happy Go Rocky\" Mascot Integration - Integrated visual and narrative cues featuring \"Rocky\" the rooster, adding a layer of wit and charm to the brand identity. 3. Interactive Text-Based Menus - Categorized digital menus (Small Plates, Large Plates, Cocktails) designed for high readability and SEO, moving away from static PDFs. 4. \"Art of Retail\" Cross-Hub - A specialized section linking to sister brands (The Bombay Canteen, Bombay Sweet Shop) to drive cross-brand loyalty and multi-site exploration. 5. Environmental Photo Hero - Full-width lifestyle banners that showcase the restaurant's \"shabby-chic\" interior details-lace curtains, cane furniture-selling the *experience* ove",
